
glossary
================

NB	- "Nota Bene" - this comment might be important, pay attention.

XXX	- this code is wrong, and needs	to be fixed
	  this should not be seen in production code

QQQ	- "Question" - the author is clueless, and is unsure whether
	   this is the best way to do something

RSN	- "Real Soon Now" - the noted functionality will be added later
	  (but don't hold your breath)

